title: I AM ATHLETE NASCAR Season 2 Premier | Brandon Marshall Sits Down with Bubba Wallace
description:
I AM ATHLETE NASCAR | Season 2: Episode 1

Bubba Wallace goes 1 on 1 with Brandon Marshal in the season premier of I AM ATHLETE NASCAR. Bubba discusses his historical win in Talladega and what it feels like to be the first African-American to win a NASCAR Cup Series playoff race since 1963.
